"# Oni \n"
"_Large giant, lawful evil_\n"
"**Armor Class** 16 (chain mail)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 110 (13d10 + 39)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft., fly 30 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/oni.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 19 (+4) | 11 (+0) | 16 (+3) | 14 (+2) | 12 (+1) | 15 (+2) |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/oni.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Saving Throws** Dex +3, Con +6, Wis +4, Cha +5    \n"
"**Skills** Arcana +5, Deception +8, Perception +4    \n"
"**Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 14    \n"
"**Languages** Common, Giant    \n"
"**Challenge** 7 (2,900 XP)  \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/oni.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Innate Spellcasting.** The oni's innate spellcasting ability is Charisma "
"(spell save DC 13). The oni can innately cast the following spells, "
"requiring no material components:    \n"
"At will: **_darkness, invisibility_**    \n"
"1/day each: **_charm person, cone of cold, gaseous form, sleep_**    \n"
"**Magic Weapons.** The oni's weapon attacks are magical.    \n"
"**Regeneration.** The oni regains 10 hit points at the start of its turn if "
"it has at least 1 hit point. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/oni.md:31
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The oni makes two attacks, either with its claws or its "
"glaive.    \n"
"**Claw (Oni Form Only).** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +7 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 8 (1d8 + 4) slashing damage.    \n"
"**Glaive.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +7 to hit, reach 10 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 15 (2d10 + 4) slashing damage, or 9 (1d10 + 4) slashing "
"damage in Small or Medium form.    \n"
"**Change Shape.** The oni magically polymorphs into a Small or Medium "
"humanoid, into a Large giant, or back into its true form. Other than its "
"size, its statistics are the same in each form. The only equipment that is "
"transformed is its glaive, which shrinks so that it can be wielded in "
"humanoid form. If the oni dies, it reverts to its true form, and its glaive "
"reverts to its normal size.\n"
msgstr ""
